Package: quarks
Type: Package
Title: Simple methods for calculating Value at Risk and Expected Shortfall
Version: 1.0.0
Maintainer: The package maintainer <sebastian.letmathe@uni-paderborn.de>
Description: This package provides the possibility to calulate Value at Risk (VaR) and Expected Shortfall (ES) 
  by means of various types of historical simulation. Currently, plain, aged and volatility weighted simulation is
  implemented in this package. Volatility weighting is carried out via an exponentially weighted moving average (EWMA).
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
